{"tid":361264,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"原來著住校服扑野真係一種情趣","createTime":"2017-08-16T03:48:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-17T08:12:05.000Z","uid":11354,"like":570,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a10a47c7805b5c3cbc3432bfadccb35ff7ce405d","tid":361264,"uid":11354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T03:48:19.000Z","msg":"同佢一齊左三年 <br />\n扑野方面真係咩花式都玩過哂 <br />\n呢排覺得自己開始無咩想搞佢既衝動 <br />\n<br />\n但就係尋晚 佢突然話想著住校服比我搞 <br />\n<br />\n我: 去邊度買校服呀? <br />\n佢: 著番我中學個套囉 <br />\n<br />\n佢係衣櫃拎左套校服出黎著左上身 <br />\n我即刻好似撻著左咁撲低左佢 <br />\n<br />\n我:一齊三年而家先知你讀慈幼 <br />\n佢: 嘻嘻 傻豬 <br />\n<br />\n就係咁 <br />\n我地就渡過左激情既夜晚 <br />\n詳細唔多講 <br />\n但我覺得我地既關係已經修補左"},{"pid":"2b9786a47987a9c0c80622afc3318d2b53926042","tid":361264,"uid":55,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T03:49:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b5b239b46d58ccf4ee02079c221ebbf64bbaa0b","tid":361264,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T03:50:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32bc3c3c78db80636856210e34a6288cc2380fcb","tid":361264,"uid":82398,"like":142,"dislike":3,"score":139,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T03:51:05.000Z","msg":"男校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f2e008c4a2c96e9d7b35ce69b7cdefd4e1e4ab6","tid":361264,"uid":64318,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T03:51:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce1a18f4451a67d877ca86c8a4ccf4e8988a9dbc","tid":361264,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T03:51:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d88d032f7358b7e37eb0a0112fcd8bf249b8ef2","tid":361264,"uid":9735,"like":187,"dislike":2,"score":185,"cit